Class Board.Builder

java.lang.Object
engine.forBoard.Board.Builder
Enclosing class:
Board
public static class Board.Builder extends Object
A builder class for constructing instances of the Board class with specific configurations. This class follows the Builder pattern to facilitate the creation of complex Board objects.
Author:
Aaron Ho, dareTo81
